729802f-a.title: Richmond: Van Duzer Street - Targee Street
729802f-a.text:
535 to 523 Van Duzer Street, east side, at Targee
Street, looking north. No. 525, the very old frame house, is
occupied(in part) by the Eagle Social Club.
July 8, 1932
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS
